      <title>Polymarket 的法国鲸鱼赢得 4800 万美元特朗普大奖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/polymarket-s-french-whale-hits-48-million-us-election-jackpot-with-trump-s-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[许多参与加密货币市场的人士周三都有理由为唐纳德·特朗普的胜利而洋洋得意，但一位备受关注的法国交易员的赌注将为选举结果带来数百万美元的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/polymarket-s-french-whale-hits-48-million-us-election-jackpot-with-trump-s-win</guid>
