      <title>加州通过零售商支持的更严厉犯罪法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/california-passes-tough-on-crime-measure-backed-by-big-retailers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州选民推翻了该州具有里程碑意义的刑事司法改革的关键内容，反映出人们对明目张胆的零售盗窃和露天吸毒行为日益增长的不满。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/california-passes-tough-on-crime-measure-backed-by-big-retailers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
